        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> This is a horrible question to ask....but what is fear kiting. I am lvl 30, and I hear people refer to it all the time. The only Fear spell I can think of is the LVL4 spell. Is fear kiting when you cast fear and just stick your pet on it, because I dont think my lvl 4 spell will work on lvl 30 creatures.  I cant root cook, because I havent hit 34 yet.  Any elaborations on Fear Kiting would be much appreciated. </P><P>Thanks as always</P><P> </font></td>

